&lt;p&gt;Here you'll find articles spanning several areas of science and
technologym focussing on fundamental aspects of the molecular sciences
and the use of programming to explore these ideas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our interests include (but are not limited to):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Molecular Quantum Mechanics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Molecular Graphics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Crystallography&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Programming Paradigms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Local and Global Optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We'll strive to post on a weekly basis. Feel free to make requests on
the comments section and, time and knowledge allowing, we'll see what
we can do!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yours trully,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team at &lt;strong&gt;AD(P)HD&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
